üî• Exam Tip (CCEE)
Keywords CDAC loves: Integrity, Chain of Custody, Forensically Sound, Admissibility
If option mentions legal compliance / evidence integrity ‚Üí usually correct
Eliminate options with speed, convenience, automation-only
